QED

Theorem env_rel_zip:
  ∀n x y xs ys.
    env_rel xs ys ∧ LIST_REL v_rel x y ∧ LENGTH n = LENGTH x ⇒
    env_rel (REVERSE(ZIP(n,x))++xs) (REVERSE(ZIP(n,y))++ys)
Proof
